## Gestione Errori e Logging

### 1. Logging Strutturato

```javascript
// Sempre con prefisso "Messages API:" per identificare facilmente
console.log("Messages API: Request started - Chat:", chat_id, "User:", userId);
console.error("Messages API: Error during credit check:", err);
```

### 2. Gestione Errori Robusta

```javascript
try {
	// Operazione principale
} catch (error) {
	console.error("Messages API: Critical error in streaming flow:", error);
	console.error("Messages API: Error stack:", error.stack);

	// Cleanup files se necessario
	if (req.files && req.files.length > 0) {
		for (const file of req.files) {
			await fs
				.unlink(file.path)
				.catch((err) =>
					console.error(`Error removing file ${file.path}:`, err)
				);
		}
	}

	// Solo invia risposta se non è già stata inviata
	if (!responseSent && !res.headersSent) {
		res.status(500).json({
			success: false,
			error: "Errore interno del server",
			details: error.message,
		});
	}
}
```

### 3. Controllo Response Sent

```javascript
let responseSent = false; // Flag per evitare doppie risposte

// Sempre controllare prima di inviare risposte
if (!responseSent) {
	res.status(201).json({ success: true, data: result });
	responseSent = true;
}
```

## Gestione File e Allegati

### 1. Upload su Google Cloud Storage

```javascript
// Step 1: Upload su GCS
const cloudResult = await cloudStorage.uploadFileFromPath(
	file.path,
	file.originalname,
	{
		folder: `chat_${chat_id}`,
		contentType: file.mimetype,
		metadata: {
			user_id: userId,
			chat_id: chat_id,
			original_name: file.originalname,
		},
	}
);

// Step 2: Salva nel database
const attachment = await Attachment.create({
	message_id: userMessage.id,
	user_id: userId,
	chat_id,
	file_type: getFileTypeFromMimeType(file.mimetype),
	file_name: cloudResult.fileName,
	original_name: file.originalname,
	file_path: cloudResult.gsUrl || cloudResult.filePath,
	file_size: cloudResult.size || file.size,
	mime_type: file.mimetype,
});

// Step 3: Cleanup file locale
await fs
	.unlink(file.path)
	.catch((err) =>
		console.warn(`Could not delete local file: ${err.message}`)
	);
```

### 2. Processamento URL per Frontend

```javascript
// Per file GCS, genera signed URL
if (attachment.file_path && attachment.file_path.startsWith("gs://")) {
	const signedUrl = await gcsService.getSignedUrl(filePath, {
		action: "read",
		expires: Date.now() + 15 * 60 * 1000, // 15 minuti
	});
	processed.downloadUrl = signedUrl;
	processed.isGcsFile = true;
} else {
	// Per file locali, costruisci URL endpoint
	processed.downloadUrl = `/api/v1/uploads/images/${attachment.file_name}`;
	processed.isGcsFile = false;
}
```

## Gestione Costi e Bilanci

### 1. Stima Costi Pre-Request

```javascript
// Service-specific cost estimation
if (modelInstance.provider?.name === "ideogram") {
	const ideogramCost = await ideogramService.calculateCost(
		modelInstance.id,
		imageCount,
		"Generate"
	);
	totalCostTokens = Math.ceil(ideogramCost.totalCost * 1000);
} else {
	// Use Python addon for text models
	const costEstimation = await pythonAddonService.getExpectedCost(
		content,
		model_id,
		"categories",
		"Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct-Turbo",
		numberOfAttachments,
		false
	);
	totalCostTokens = pythonAddonService.extractTotalCostTokens(costEstimation);
}
```

### 2. Controllo Bilancio

```javascript
// Check user balance against cost estimate
if (!wallet || wallet.balance < totalCostTokens) {
	console.warn(`Messages API: Insufficient funds for user ${userId}`);
	return res.status(402).json({
		success: false,
		error: "Fondi insufficienti",
		details: `Costo stimato: ${totalCostTokens} crediti`,
	});
}
```

### 3. Calcolo Costi Post-Response

```javascript
// Skip cost calculation for special providers
if (modelInstance.provider?.name === "ideogram") {
	finalCost = {
		total_cost_for_user: 0, // Already deducted by service
		total_cost_aigens: 0,
		// ... altri campi
	};
} else {
	const costCalculator = new CostCalculator();
	finalCost = await costCalculator.calculateCost({
		provider: providerName,
		modelId: modelInstance.id,
		apiModelId: model_id,
		inputTokens: inputTokens,
		outputTokens: outputTokens,
	});
}
```

## Streaming e SSE

### 1. Rilevamento Modalità Streaming

```javascript
const useStreaming =
	req.headers.accept === "text/event-stream" ||
	req.headers["x-streaming"] === "true";

if (useStreaming) {
	res.writeHead(200, {
		"Content-Type": "text/event-stream",
		"Cache-Control": "no-cache",
		Connection: "keep-alive",
		"X-Accel-Buffering": "no",
	});

	sendEvent = (type, data) => {
		if (!res.finished) {
			res.write(`data: ${JSON.stringify({ type, ...data })}\n\n`);
		}
	};
}
```

### 2. Eventi Streaming

```javascript
sendEvent("process_started", {
	message: "Inizializzazione della richiesta...",
});
sendEvent("delta", { text: chunk });
sendEvent("completed", { text: fullText, cost: finalCost });
sendEvent("error", { error: "Errore AI", details: err.message });
```

## Risoluzione Servizi AI

### 1. Pattern di Risoluzione

```javascript
// Usa sempre modelService.resolveStreamingService
const serviceInfo = await modelService.resolveStreamingService(model_id);

// Map service name to actual service object
switch (serviceInfo.service) {
	case "anthropicService":
		aiService = anthropicService;
		break;
	case "openaiService":
		aiService = openaiService;
		break;
	// ... altri casi
	default:
		throw new Error(`Servizio non supportato: ${serviceInfo.service}`);
}
```

### 2. Gestione Errori Specifici

```javascript
if (error.message.includes("Model not found")) {
	throw new Error(`Modello non trovato nel database: ${model_id}`);
} else if (error.message.includes("Provider not found")) {
	throw new Error(`Provider non trovato per il modello: ${model_id}`);
} else if (error.message.includes("No streaming service available")) {
	throw new Error(
		`Nessun servizio di streaming disponibile per il modello: ${model_id}`
	);
}
```

